1
00:00:25,008 --> 00:00:25,976
(yue)嗰一日
(en)That day

2
00:00:26,787 --> 00:00:28,119
(yue)人類記返起…
(en)Humans remembered...

3
00:00:34,755 --> 00:00:37,094
(yue)一直畀佢哋支配嘅恐懼
(en)The fear that had always ruled over them

4
00:00:40,282 --> 00:00:42,292
(yue)同有如韞喺鳥籠入面嘅…
(en)And the humiliation of being trapped in a birdcage-like state...

5
00:00:43,442 --> 00:00:44,388
(yue)屈辱
(en)Humiliation

6
00:01:03,338 --> 00:01:04,600
(yue)準備作戰
(en)Prepare for battle

7
00:01:05,672 --> 00:01:08,371
(yue)目標第一個，一定要將佢殺死
(en)The first target, make sure to kill it

8
00:01:08,439 --> 00:01:11,760
(yue)務必令到呢度變化我哋人類一牆外嘅據點
(en)Ensure this place becomes humanity's foothold beyond the walls

9
00:01:12,657 --> 00:01:13,784
(yue)目標接近
(en)The target is approaching

10
00:01:19,383 --> 00:01:21,526
(yue)同訓練嗰陣一樣兵分兩路
(en)Just like training, split into two groups

11
00:01:22,222 --> 00:01:24,266
(yue)照計劃由我哋呢組做餌
(en)As planned, our group will act as bait

12
00:01:24,524 --> 00:01:27,078
(yue)攻擊組即刻進行立體機動攻擊
(en)The attack group will launch a three-dimensional maneuver attack immediately

13
00:01:49,062 --> 00:01:50,780
(yue)全部位同時攻擊
(en)Attack all positions simultaneously

14
00:01:56,612 --> 00:01:58,663
(yue)就畀你見識下我哋人類嘅…
(en)Let me show you humanity's...

15
00:01:59,384 --> 00:02:00,297
(yue)力量！
(en)Power!

16
00:03:34,065 --> 00:03:38,848
(yue)《致二千年後的你：西甘希娜淪陷1》
(en)“To You, 2000 Years Later: The Fall of Shiganshina Part 1”

17
00:04:06,238 --> 00:04:08,331
(yue)係…米卡莎
(en)It’s… Mikasa

18
00:04:09,313 --> 00:04:10,699
(yue)我哋要返去喇
(en)We need to go back

19
00:04:12,137 --> 00:04:14,086
(yue)你點會喺度𠸏？
(en)What are you doing here?

20
00:04:15,517 --> 00:04:17,873
(yue)你係唔係到而家都仲未瞓醒啊？
(en)Are you still not awake yet?

21
00:04:18,456 --> 00:04:20,818
(yue)唔係，不過…
(en)No, but…

22
00:04:20,894 --> 00:04:23,694
(yue)我好似發咗個好長同埋好恐怖嘅夢
(en)I think I had a long and terrifying dream

23
00:04:26,173 --> 00:04:27,591
(yue)夢見啲咩呢？
(en)What did you dream about?

24
00:04:28,197 --> 00:04:29,411
(yue)諗唔起啊
(en)I can’t remember

25
00:04:33,837 --> 00:04:36,005
(yue)艾倫，你做咩喊啊？
(en)Eren, why are you crying?

26
00:04:41,147 --> 00:04:43,308
(yue)（845年，西甘希娜）
(en)(Year 845, Shiganshina)

27
00:04:47,648 --> 00:04:48,688
(yue)記住
(en)Remember

28
00:04:48,766 --> 00:04:51,531
(yue)城牆係由神嘅智慧興建出嚟㗎
(en)The walls were built by God’s wisdom

29
00:04:51,984 --> 00:04:55,242
(yue)所以城牆就係神喺世上施嘅神跡
(en)So the walls are God’s miracle on Earth

30
00:04:55,588 --> 00:04:59,194
(yue)無論係邊個，都絕對唔可以沾污城牆
(en)No one is allowed to defile the walls

31
00:05:02,389 --> 00:05:03,656
(yue)唔准同你講啊
(en)You can’t tell anyone

32
00:05:04,722 --> 00:05:06,414
(yue)邊個都絕對唔講得
(en)Don’t tell anyone, no matter who

33
00:05:06,786 --> 00:05:07,707
(yue)我知喇
(en)I understand

34
00:05:08,650 --> 00:05:11,652
(yue)但係，你無端端流眼淚
(en)But suddenly you started crying

35
00:05:12,324 --> 00:05:14,254
(yue)不如叫你爸爸睇下啦
(en)How about letting your dad take a look?

36
00:05:14,555 --> 00:05:15,628
(yue)正蠢材
(en)That’s stupid

37
00:05:15,888 --> 00:05:17,960
(yue)咁尷尬，唔會啲點同爸爸講
(en)That’s embarrassing, no way I’d tell Dad

38
00:05:18,067 --> 00:05:19,917
(yue)做咩流眼淚啊？艾倫
(en)Why are you crying, Eren?

39
00:05:22,317 --> 00:05:23,572
(yue)漢尼斯叔叔
(en)Uncle Hannes

40
00:05:23,959 --> 00:05:26,308
(yue)你係咪發米卡莎嘅脾氣啊？
(en)Did you upset Mikasa?

41
00:05:27,237 --> 00:05:28,985
(yue)你唔知，唔好亂講啦
(en)You don’t know, don’t talk nonsense

42
00:05:29,514 --> 00:05:30,922
(yue)好大𠹻酒𡃴啊
(en)What a drunkard

43
00:05:32,443 --> 00:05:34,295
(yue)得閒飲返杯真係過癮
(en)Having a drink when free is really enjoyable

44
00:05:35,078 --> 00:05:36,343
(yue)佢哋又係噉
(en)There they go again

45
00:05:36,475 --> 00:05:38,484
(yue)你想唔想過嚟一齊飲啊？
(en)Do you want to come drink with us?

46
00:05:38,545 --> 00:05:41,070
(yue)唔好，你今日負責咩啊？
(en)No, what’s your duty today?

47
00:05:41,131 --> 00:05:43,338
(yue)我？負責守城門喇
(en)Me? Guarding the gate

48
00:05:43,663 --> 00:05:46,084
(yue)成日流流長，又無所事事
(en)Always idling around, doing nothing

49
00:05:46,145 --> 00:05:48,631
(yue)梗係覺得肚餓又會口渴㗎喇
(en)Of course, you’d feel hungry and thirsty

50
00:05:49,268 --> 00:05:52,511
(yue)好似噉樣加少少酒落嘢飲都冇所謂喇
(en)Adding a bit of alcohol to your drink is fine

51
00:05:52,627 --> 00:05:54,753
(yue)橫掂我哋都冇嘢好做
(en)We have nothing else to do anyway
52
00:05:56,103 --> 00:05:58,523
(yue)萬一有事發生，你哋都做戰鬥到咩？
(en)If something happens, can you even fight?

53
00:06:00,058 --> 00:06:02,650
-到底會有咩事發生啊？
-仲使問？
(en)-What could possibly happen?  
-Do you even need to ask?

54
00:06:03,001 --> 00:06:06,136
(yue)嗰啲嘢破壞城牆走入嚟就要靠你哋收拾㗎喇
(en)If those things break through the walls, it’ll be up to you to handle them

55
00:06:07,827 --> 00:06:09,198
(yue)呢條魚好新鮮㗎
(en)This fish is really fresh

56
00:06:10,129 --> 00:06:11,271
(yue)復咗嚟
(en)I just caught it

57
00:06:11,416 --> 00:06:12,476
(yue)喂，艾倫
(en)Hey, Eren

58
00:06:12,573 --> 00:06:14,492
(yue)咪失驚無神大聲嗌啊
(en)Stop shouting all of a sudden

59
00:06:16,067 --> 00:06:18,134
(yue)醫生個仔好活潑喎
(en)The doctor’s son is really energetic

60
00:06:18,811 --> 00:06:22,983
(yue)如果佢哋真係可以攻入城牆裏面嘅  
我哋收會收拾佢哋
(en)If they really invade the walls, we’ll deal with them

61
00:06:23,253 --> 00:06:25,041
(yue)之不過你擔心嘅呢一種事
(en)But the thing you’re worried about

62
00:06:25,102 --> 00:06:27,372
(yue)根本成百年以嚟都冇發生過
(en)Hasn’t happened in a hundred years

63
00:06:27,484 --> 00:06:31,218
(yue)我爸爸話：  
“意外通常發生係人最安心鬆懈嘅時候  
唔可以大意㗎”
(en)My dad says:  
"Disasters happen when people are most relaxed.  
You can’t let your guard down.”

64
00:06:33,191 --> 00:06:35,047
(yue)乜醫生噉樣講過咩？
(en)The doctor really said that?

65
00:06:35,317 --> 00:06:36,745
(yue)噉實有佢嘅道理
(en)There must be some truth to it

66
00:06:37,238 --> 00:06:41,325
(yue)話晒佢以前都醫返好晒呢一度患咗流行病嘅人
(en)After all, he once cured everyone here of an epidemic

67
00:06:41,834 --> 00:06:43,779
(yue)佢當然叻過我好多喇
(en)He’s obviously much smarter than me

68
00:06:44,310 --> 00:06:46,858
(yue)不過對嗰啲嘢嘅認識就例外
(en)But his knowledge about those things is an exception

69
00:06:48,621 --> 00:06:52,717
(yue)我當咗兵之後  
有陣時要輪流幫城牆做例行維修工作
(en)After becoming a soldier,  
I sometimes help with routine wall maintenance

70
00:06:52,778 --> 00:06:54,992
(yue)所以見過嗰啲嘢喺外邊行
(en)So I’ve seen those things walking outside

71
00:06:55,466 --> 00:07:00,310
(yue)我唔認為佢哋有能力破壞  
或者嗰度呢一大幅有成50米高嘅牆
(en)I don’t think they can destroy  
this massive 50-meter-high wall

72
00:07:00,897 --> 00:07:01,811
(yue)唔通
(en)Unless…

73
00:07:01,992 --> 00:07:04,803
(yue)你哋一直以嚟從來都冇諗過同嗰啲嘢戰鬥？
(en)Have you never thought of fighting those things?

74
00:07:05,365 --> 00:07:06,414
(yue)梗係冇喇
(en)Of course not

75
00:07:07,413 --> 00:07:08,620
(yue)有冇搞錯？
(en)Are you kidding me?

76
00:07:08,922 --> 00:07:11,129
(yue)噉你哋班人仲叫咩駐紮兵團啊？
(en)How can you still call yourselves the Garrison Regiment?

77
00:07:11,198 --> 00:07:13,072
(yue)索性叫城牆維修隊吖
(en)Might as well call yourselves the Wall Repair Team

78
00:07:13,159 --> 00:07:14,828
(yue)個名叫好聽喎
(en)It’s a fitting name, isn’t it?

79
00:07:16,313 --> 00:07:18,145
(yue)不過，艾倫，你要明白
(en)But, Eren, you need to understand

80
00:07:18,206 --> 00:07:21,573
(yue)需要士兵出動嘅時候就代表情況變得好惡劣
(en)When soldiers are needed, it means things have turned dire

81
00:07:22,412 --> 00:07:24,306
(yue)相反當士兵畀人笑
(en)On the contrary, when soldiers are mocked

82
00:07:24,367 --> 00:07:27,107
(yue)遊手好閒、白逗人工、一無是處
(en)For being idle and useless freeloaders

83
00:07:27,168 --> 00:07:28,791
(yue)就代表大家生活安穩
(en)It means everyone is living in peace
84
00:07:31,914 --> 00:07:32,914
(yue)即係…
(en)So that means...

85
00:07:33,875 --> 00:07:35,466
(yue)就算一世走唔出城牆
(en)Even if we never leave the walls our entire lives

86
00:07:36,367 --> 00:07:38,190
(yue)只要有得食同瞓就夠？
(en)As long as we have food and sleep, that’s enough?

87
00:07:39,457 --> 00:07:41,765
(yue)但係，咁簡直就係…
(en)But that’s just...

88
00:07:42,988 --> 00:07:44,963
(yue)同安全嘅畜生冇分別
(en)No different from being safe livestock

89
00:07:48,664 --> 00:07:50,861
(yue)呢個細路講嘢就好有種
(en)This kid talks so boldly

90
00:07:50,922 --> 00:07:52,650
(yue)自己就咩都做唔到
(en)Yet he can’t do anything himself

91
00:07:52,791 --> 00:07:54,502
(yue)係咪係啊，漢尼斯？
(en)Isn’t that right, Hannes?

92
00:07:55,143 --> 00:07:56,224
(yue)哦，係啊
(en)Oh, yeah

93
00:07:57,998 --> 00:07:59,812
(yue)喂！艾倫！
(en)Hey! Eren!

94
00:08:01,213 --> 00:08:02,396
(yue)古靈精怪
(en)You little rascal

95
00:08:03,727 --> 00:08:05,148
(yue)唔通艾倫佢…
(en)Could it be that Eren...

96
00:08:05,396 --> 00:08:07,912
(yue)大個之後想加入調查兵團？
(en)Wants to join the Scout Regiment when he grows up?

97
00:08:17,034 --> 00:08:20,188
(yue)艾倫，你都係唔好加入調查兵團啊
(en)Eren, you really shouldn’t join the Scout Regiment

98
00:08:21,265 --> 00:08:22,208
(yue)點解啊？
(en)Why?

99
00:08:22,269 --> 00:08:24,261
(yue)唔通你呢度睇唔起調查兵團？
(en)Don’t tell me you look down on the Scouts?

100
00:08:24,654 --> 00:08:27,167
(yue)呢個根本就唔係睇唔睇得起嘅問題
(en)This isn’t about respect or lack of it

101
00:08:34,332 --> 00:08:36,217
(yue)調查兵團，佢哋返嚟喇
(en)The Scouts, they’re back

102
00:08:36,678 --> 00:08:38,477
(yue)城牆嘅大門要打開
(en)The gates of the wall need to open

103
00:08:38,538 --> 00:08:40,905
(yue)行啦，米卡莎，我哋迎接英雄
(en)Let’s go, Mikasa. Let’s welcome the heroes

104
00:08:53,863 --> 00:08:56,016
(yue)咁多人嘅，睇唔到𠻹
(en)There’s so many people, I can’t see

105
00:09:24,824 --> 00:09:27,107
(yue)一大班人去到返咁少人返
(en)A large group went out, but so few returned

106
00:09:27,308 --> 00:09:29,168
(yue)慌唔係畀嗰啲嘢食咗咩
(en)Could they have been eaten by those things?

107
00:09:29,229 --> 00:09:31,140
(yue)無情情走咗城牆外邊
(en)Going outside the walls recklessly

108
00:09:31,201 --> 00:09:32,967
(yue)就會有噉個下場呢
(en)Leads to an end like this

109
00:09:33,884 --> 00:09:36,303
(yue)莫杰斯…
(en)Moses...

110
00:09:36,628 --> 00:09:38,143
(yue)請問咁多位
(en)Excuse me, everyone

111
00:09:38,253 --> 00:09:40,658
(yue)你哋有冇見過我仔莫杰斯啊？
(en)Have you seen my son Moses?

112
00:09:40,799 --> 00:09:42,819
(yue)我仔而家到底喺邊度啊？
(en)Where is my son right now?

113
00:09:44,077 --> 00:09:45,918
(yue)你就係莫杰斯嘅媽媽？
(en)Are you Moses’s mother?

114
00:09:46,411 --> 00:09:47,395
(yue)你畀佢
(en)Give this to her

115
00:10:13,503 --> 00:10:16,779
(yue)真係好對唔住，我哋只係帶到咁多返嚟
(en)I’m so sorry, this is all we could bring back

116
00:10:34,026 --> 00:10:37,375
(yue)不過…我個仔真係好有用
(en)But... my son was truly useful

117
00:10:39,263 --> 00:10:42,300
(yue)就算個冇直接粒都咩功都冇關係
(en)Even if he didn’t contribute directly, it doesn’t matter

118
00:10:42,589 --> 00:10:44,742
(yue)我個仔莫杰斯嘅死係唔係…
(en)Didn’t my son Moses’s death...

119
00:10:44,803 --> 00:10:47,465
(yue)對人類第日嘅反攻有好大貢獻啊
(en)Make a huge contribution to humanity’s future counterattack?

120
00:10:54,413 --> 00:10:55,771
(yue)咁當然係喇
(en)Of course, it did
121
00:10:59,595 --> 00:11:00,590
(yue)唔係
(en)No

122
00:11:01,673 --> 00:11:03,262
(yue)我哋呢一次調查…
(en)This time on the expedition...

123
00:11:03,772 --> 00:11:04,530
(yue)我哋…
(en)We...

124
00:11:05,190 --> 00:11:06,145
(yue)仍然…
(en)Still...

125
00:11:06,538 --> 00:11:07,685
(yue)仲係…
(en)Remain...

126
00:11:10,333 --> 00:11:13,777
(yue)我哋呢一次調查仍然係冇成果啊
(en)This expedition still yielded no results

127
00:11:15,007 --> 00:11:16,793
(yue)一切都係因為我冇能
(en)It’s all because of my incompetence

128
00:11:17,293 --> 00:11:19,433
(yue)令到好多士兵白白噉犧牲
(en)That so many soldiers died in vain

129
00:11:20,386 --> 00:11:22,151
(yue)到而家都仲係唔知道…
(en)Even now, we still don’t know...

130
00:11:22,806 --> 00:11:24,462
(yue)佢哋嘅真面目係點樣
(en)What their true nature is

131
00:11:24,523 --> 00:11:27,029
(yue)我哋根本咩都查唔到啊
(en)We haven’t found out anything at all

132
00:11:33,094 --> 00:11:34,529
(yue)真係好陰功啊
(en)It’s truly a tragedy

133
00:11:34,597 --> 00:11:35,675
(yue)話咗㗎喇
(en)I already said it

134
00:11:36,265 --> 00:11:38,204
(yue)調查兵團出去做乜嘢啊？
(en)What’s the point of the Scouts going out there?

135
00:11:38,265 --> 00:11:40,888
(yue)我哋交稅養啲噉個人啊，我哋仲應該…
(en)We pay taxes to support these people, and we’re supposed to...

136
00:11:44,637 --> 00:11:46,357
(yue)做咩啊，細路？做咩打我？
(en)What’s wrong, kid? Why did you hit me?

137
00:11:48,434 --> 00:11:49,345
(yue)喂
(en)Hey

138
00:11:49,406 --> 00:11:50,757
(yue)放開我，米卡莎！
(en)Let me go, Mikasa!

139
00:11:50,818 --> 00:11:52,872
(yue)喂，細路，你咪走啊，細路
(en)Hey, kid, don’t run, kid

140
00:11:55,336 --> 00:11:57,211
(yue)米卡莎，放開我吖！
(en)Mikasa, let me go!

141
00:12:03,390 --> 00:12:04,565
(yue)你到底做咩啊？
(en)What are you doing?

142
00:12:04,626 --> 00:12:06,180
(yue)搞到我跌晒啲柴喇
(en)You made me drop all the firewood

143
00:12:07,602 --> 00:12:08,490
(yue)艾倫
(en)Eren

144
00:12:08,982 --> 00:12:11,580
(yue)你到而家都仲係好想加入調查兵團
(en)You still want to join the Scout Regiment

145
00:12:11,641 --> 00:12:12,747
(yue)係唔係啊？
(en)Don’t you?

146
00:12:21,046 --> 00:12:23,260
(yue)可唔可以幫手執啊？
(en)Can you help me pick these up?

147
00:12:24,555 --> 00:12:26,141
(yue)咁小事都要幫？
(en)Do you even need help with such a small thing?

148
00:12:28,086 --> 00:12:30,668
(yue)（而家可以公開嘅情報關於牆壁1）  
（人類喺三幅城牆內生活）
(en)(Now Public Information About the Walls 1)  
(Humans live within three walls)

149
00:12:30,729 --> 00:12:33,197
(yue)（第一幅叫瑪莉亞之牆）  
（第二幅叫露絲之牆）  
（第三幅叫仙娜）
(en)(The first is Wall Maria)  
(The second is Wall Rose)  
(The third is Wall Sina)

150
00:12:33,258 --> 00:12:35,210
(yue)（而家可以公開嘅情報關於牆壁2）  
（牆壁之間嘅面積大致相等）
(en)(Now Public Information About the Walls 2)  
(The areas between the walls are roughly equal)

151
00:12:35,271 --> 00:12:37,810
(yue)（瑪莉亞同露絲之間距離100公里）  
（露絲同仙娜之間距離130公里）  
（仙娜同中心點距離250公里）
(en)(The distance between Maria and Rose is 100 km)  
(The distance between Rose and Sina is 130 km)  
(The distance from Sina to the center is 250 km)
152
00:12:43,301 --> 00:12:44,259
(yue)我哋返嚟喇
(en)We’re back

153
00:12:46,213 --> 00:12:47,354
(yue)你哋返嚟喇
(en)You’re back

154
00:12:50,839 --> 00:12:52,053
(yue)好嘢喎，艾倫
(en)Good job, Eren

155
00:12:52,114 --> 00:12:54,370
(yue)今日咁勤力執到咁多柴啊？
(en)You worked so hard today to collect this much firewood?

156
00:12:54,690 --> 00:12:55,721
(yue)哦，係啊
(en)Oh, yeah

157
00:12:59,446 --> 00:13:00,873
(yue)做咩掹我耳仔啊？
(en)Why are you pulling my ear?

158
00:13:00,934 --> 00:13:04,253
(yue)你啲耳仔紅晒喇，證明你有嘢瞞住我
(en)Your ears are all red, proving you’re hiding something from me

159
00:13:04,377 --> 00:13:06,324
(yue)啲柴係唔係米卡莎執嘎？
(en)Wasn’t the firewood collected by Mikasa?

160
00:13:08,839 --> 00:13:10,129
(yue)爸爸又要出門呀？
(en)Dad is going out again?

161
00:13:11,036 --> 00:13:12,661
-有嘢要做？  
-係啊
(en)-Is there something you need to do?  
-Yes

162
00:13:12,966 --> 00:13:14,359
(yue)我要去內陸應診
(en)I have to go to the interior for a consultation

163
00:13:14,653 --> 00:13:16,237
(yue)大概去兩三日到喇
(en)I’ll be gone for about two or three days

164
00:13:19,433 --> 00:13:22,580
(yue)艾倫話大個之後要加入調查兵團
(en)Eren said he wants to join the Scout Regiment when he grows up

165
00:13:27,779 --> 00:13:29,977
-米卡莎，做乜嘢講？  
-艾倫
(en)-Mikasa, why did you say that?  
-Eren

166
00:13:30,729 --> 00:13:32,380
(yue)你個腦諗緊啲乜嘢啊？
(en)What are you thinking?

167
00:13:32,449 --> 00:13:36,581
(yue)你知唔知道有幾多人走出城牆外面  
結果搞到自己連命都冇埋？
(en)Do you know how many people left the walls  
only to end up losing their lives?

168
00:13:36,642 --> 00:13:37,866
(yue)我梗係知喇
(en)Of course I know

169
00:13:37,927 --> 00:13:39,728
-係噉點解？  
-艾倫
(en)-Then why?  
-Eren

170
00:13:41,744 --> 00:13:44,292
(yue)點解你想走出到個城牆外面？
(en)Why do you want to go outside the walls?

171
00:13:45,848 --> 00:13:47,406
(yue)因為我想知道
(en)Because I want to know

172
00:13:47,467 --> 00:13:49,718
(yue)城牆外面嘅世界到底係點樣
(en)What the world outside the walls is really like

173
00:13:50,333 --> 00:13:53,584
(yue)我唔想一世咩都唔知根本喺城牆入面
(en)I don’t want to spend my life knowing nothing inside these walls

174
00:13:54,610 --> 00:13:55,523
(yue)而且…
(en)And...

175
00:13:56,459 --> 00:13:58,522
(yue)冇人繼續調查兵團嘅工作
(en)If no one continues the Scouts’ work

176
00:13:59,554 --> 00:14:02,286
(yue)噉之前為咗人類而死嘅人就會白白犧牲！
(en)Then the people who died for humanity will have sacrificed in vain!

177
00:14:06,594 --> 00:14:07,601
(yue)我明白喇
(en)I understand

178
00:14:09,895 --> 00:14:12,011
(yue)我夠鐘搭船，我要出去喇
(en)It’s time for me to board the ship, I have to go

179
00:14:12,455 --> 00:14:14,953
(yue)等陣啊，老公，你勸阿艾倫吖
(en)Wait, dear, you should talk to Eren

180
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:18,500
(yue)卡露拉，人類擁有嘅好奇心…
(en)Carla, humanity’s curiosity...

181
00:14:18,925 --> 00:14:21,758
(yue)並唔會因為其他人三言兩語就可以撳得住
(en)Can’t be suppressed by a few words from others

182
00:14:22,705 --> 00:14:23,478
(yue)艾倫
(en)Eren

183
00:14:25,002 --> 00:14:29,552
(yue)我返嚟之後，就帶你去過間  
(yue)直冇帶你去過個地下室喇
(en)When I come back, I’ll take you to the basement  
(en)I’ve never taken you to before

184
00:14:30,500 --> 00:14:31,875
(yue)你講真𠸏？
(en)Are you serious?

185
00:14:36,040 --> 00:14:37,700
(yue)早去早回吖
(en)Go and come back soon

186
00:14:40,055 --> 00:14:41,008
(yue)我唔批准
(en)I don’t approve

187
00:14:42,350 --> 00:14:44,484
(yue)我唔會畀你咁蠢加入調查兵團
(en)I won’t let you foolishly join the Scout Regiment

188
00:14:45,346 --> 00:14:46,547
(yue)你話噉樣係蠢？
(en)You think that’s foolish?

189
00:14:46,623 --> 00:14:47,553
(yue)我話嗰啲
(en)I’m saying those

190
00:14:47,614 --> 00:14:50,141
(yue)甘於過安穩生活做畜牲嘅人至係蠢吖
(en)Who are content living as safe livestock are the foolish ones
191
00:14:51,790 --> 00:14:52,594
(yue)艾倫
(en)Eren

192
00:14:56,121 --> 00:14:57,047
(yue)米卡莎
(en)Mikasa

193
00:14:57,462 --> 00:14:59,710
(yue)你都知艾倫份人好容易闖禍
(en)You know Eren gets into trouble easily

194
00:14:59,771 --> 00:15:01,408
(yue)所以麻煩你幫我睇住佢
(en)So I need you to watch over him

195
00:15:01,469 --> 00:15:02,789
(yue)唔好畀佢出事啊
(en)Make sure he stays safe

196
00:15:07,449 --> 00:15:08,885
(yue)點啊，異端？
(en)What’s wrong, heretic?

197
00:15:10,282 --> 00:15:12,416
(yue)你唔服氣嘅就快還手啦
(en)If you’re upset, fight back already

198
00:15:13,845 --> 00:15:15,856
(yue)我先至唔會做啲噉樣嘅事啊
(en)I would never do something like that

199
00:15:15,917 --> 00:15:18,006
(yue)否則我就會同你哋一樣講野蠻
(en)Otherwise, I’d be as barbaric as you

200
00:15:18,067 --> 00:15:19,091
(yue)講咩話？
(en)What did you say?

201
00:15:19,172 --> 00:15:22,438
(yue)你哋喺心入面其實以為我講嘅嘢係啱嘅
(en)Deep down, you know I’m right

202
00:15:22,518 --> 00:15:25,159
(yue)因為拗唔贏我所以你哋先出手打我
(en)You hit me because you can’t win the argument

203
00:15:26,264 --> 00:15:28,995
(yue)亦即係你哋一早已經向我投咗降
(en)That means you’ve already surrendered to me

204
00:15:30,217 --> 00:15:32,794
(yue)收聲吖，你唔好再狡辯吖！
(en)Shut up, stop making excuses!

205
00:15:32,855 --> 00:15:33,958
(yue)停手吖！
(en)Stop it!

206
00:15:36,399 --> 00:15:37,264
(yue)艾倫啊
(en)Eren

207
00:15:37,733 --> 00:15:39,592
(yue)嗰個蠢材自己送上門啝
(en)That idiot came right to us

208
00:15:39,653 --> 00:15:41,069
(yue)我要打到佢甩牙
(en)I’m going to knock his teeth out

209
00:15:41,130 --> 00:15:42,445
(yue)好好教訓到佢
(en)Teach him a proper lesson

210
00:15:43,862 --> 00:15:45,307
(yue)係…係米卡莎
(en)It’s... it’s Mikasa

211
00:15:46,412 --> 00:15:48,221
(yue)唔掂啊，快啲走啊！
(en)We’re in trouble, run!

212
00:15:48,286 --> 00:15:49,111
(yue)走啊
(en)Run!

213
00:15:53,118 --> 00:15:54,168
(yue)冇膽鬼
(en)Cowards

214
00:15:54,229 --> 00:15:56,863
(yue)佢哋一見到我，就即刻走夾唔抖喇
(en)The moment they saw me, they ran away in panic

215
00:15:57,205 --> 00:15:59,988
(yue)唔係啊，係見到米卡莎先走㗎
(en)No, they ran because they saw Mikasa

216
00:16:02,149 --> 00:16:03,262
(yue)點啊，阿爾敏？
(en)What’s wrong, Armin?

217
00:16:07,699 --> 00:16:09,347
(yue)我可以自己起身
(en)I can get up on my own

218
00:16:10,112 --> 00:16:11,061
(yue)好啦
(en)Alright

219
00:16:14,371 --> 00:16:16,628
(yue)噉跟住，我就同佢哋講
(en)So then, I told them

220
00:16:16,689 --> 00:16:19,046
(yue)人類仲有一日會走出外面嘅世界
(en)One day, humanity will venture out into the world

221
00:16:19,632 --> 00:16:21,642
(yue)我哋就打我，鬧我異端
(en)They hit me and called me a heretic

222
00:16:21,703 --> 00:16:22,528
(yue)衰人
(en)Jerks

223
00:16:24,703 --> 00:16:26,674
(yue)只不過係話要走出外面吒嘛
(en)I just said we should go outside

224
00:16:26,735 --> 00:16:28,372
(yue)點解就要畀人歧視喎？
(en)Why does that make me a target?

225
00:16:28,433 --> 00:16:29,623
(yue)係因為…
(en)Is it because...

226
00:16:29,995 --> 00:16:31,705
(yue)喺牆入面嘅呢一百年
(en)In these hundred years inside the walls

227
00:16:31,766 --> 00:16:33,845
(yue)大家嘅生活都過得好安穩
(en)Everyone has lived such peaceful lives

228
00:16:34,137 --> 00:16:36,806
(yue)所以大家都驚派人出外面嘅話
(en)So they’re afraid that sending people outside

229
00:16:36,862 --> 00:16:39,259
(yue)會將嗰啲嘢有外面引到牆入面
(en)Will attract those things from outside into the walls

230
00:16:39,320 --> 00:16:41,517
(yue)而且國王政府一向方針
(en)And the government’s policy has always been

231
00:16:41,708 --> 00:16:44,883
(yue)就係將去探索牆外面世界當係最大禁忌
(en)To treat exploring the outside world as the greatest taboo
232
00:16:45,535 --> 00:16:47,375
(yue)要點用我哋自己條命
(en)How we use our lives

233
00:16:47,534 --> 00:16:48,767
(yue)係我哋嘅自由
(en)Is our own freedom

234
00:16:48,828 --> 00:16:50,208
(yue)我唔准你噉諗
(en)I won’t allow you to think like that

235
00:16:52,190 --> 00:16:53,160
(yue)唔准
(en)No way

236
00:16:53,745 --> 00:16:54,932
(yue)我都仲未話你啊
(en)I haven’t even started with you

237
00:16:54,983 --> 00:16:56,578
(yue)竟然同我父母講
(en)You actually told my parents

238
00:16:57,531 --> 00:16:59,435
(yue)你冇叫我隱瞞呢件事
(en)You never told me to keep it a secret

239
00:16:59,952 --> 00:17:01,149
(yue)隱瞞咩啊？
(en)Keep what a secret?

240
00:17:01,483 --> 00:17:02,705
(yue)嗰件事…
(en)That thing...

241
00:17:02,848 --> 00:17:04,546
(yue)我而家冇心情講
(en)I’m not in the mood to talk about it now

242
00:17:04,928 --> 00:17:07,189
(yue)係呀？噉就算喇
(en)Is that so? Then fine

243
00:17:11,711 --> 00:17:12,553
(yue)講真…
(en)Honestly...

244
00:17:13,449 --> 00:17:14,967
(yue)盲目相信城牆
(en)Blindly believing in the walls

245
00:17:15,028 --> 00:17:16,761
(yue)可以永遠保護我哋嘅安全
(en)Can always keep us safe

246
00:17:16,822 --> 00:17:18,393
(yue)真係太荒謬喇
(en)Is utterly absurd

247
00:17:22,441 --> 00:17:25,605
(yue)就算城牆喺之前一百年都冇出過事
(en)Even if nothing happened to the walls in the past 100 years

248
00:17:26,029 --> 00:17:28,121
(yue)都唔等於呢一大幅城牆
(en)It doesn’t mean these massive walls

249
00:17:30,267 --> 00:17:31,883
(yue)今日唔會出事
(en)Won’t fail today

250
00:17:46,526 --> 00:17:48,020
(yue)咩事啊？咩啊？
(en)What’s going on? What’s that?

251
00:17:48,756 --> 00:17:49,677
(yue)好大聲啊
(en)It’s so loud

252
00:17:51,496 --> 00:17:52,536
(yue)咩事啊？
(en)What happened?

253
00:17:52,597 --> 00:17:53,551
(yue)係爆炸？
(en)Was that an explosion?

254
00:17:54,994 --> 00:17:57,597
(yue)嗰度啊，好似有嘢跌落嚟啊  
-過睇下
(en)Over there, something seems to have fallen  
-Let’s go take a look

255
00:17:59,947 --> 00:18:01,733
(yue)喂，等埋，阿爾敏
(en)Hey, wait up, Armin

256
00:18:05,106 --> 00:18:06,320
(yue)咩事啊？
(en)What’s wrong?

257
00:18:06,622 --> 00:18:08,582
(yue)大家企定定望緊啲咩啊？
(en)Why is everyone standing still staring?

258
00:18:18,778 --> 00:18:21,259
(yue)唔係啩，幅牆…
(en)No way, the wall...

259
00:18:21,982 --> 00:18:23,974
(yue)有成50米咁高㗎
(en)It’s 50 meters high

260
00:18:25,609 --> 00:18:26,728
(yue)係嗰啲嘢
(en)It’s those things

261
00:18:32,784 --> 00:18:33,839
(yue)係巨人
(en)It’s a Titan

262
00:19:20,628 --> 00:19:21,740
(yue)城牆…
(en)The wall...

263
00:19:23,183 --> 00:19:24,922
(yue)畀巨人踢穿咗個大窿
(en)Has been kicked open by a Titan

264
00:19:30,714 --> 00:19:32,364
(yue)係巨人入進嚟啊！
(en)A Titan has entered!

265
00:19:33,016 --> 00:19:33,960
(yue)走吖！
(en)Run!

266
00:19:37,215 --> 00:19:38,372
(yue)快啲走啦
(en)Hurry up and run

267
00:19:39,230 --> 00:19:40,079
(yue)艾倫
(en)Eren

268
00:19:40,404 --> 00:19:41,650
(yue)係我屋企嗰邊啊
(en)It’s near my house

269
00:19:42,254 --> 00:19:43,181
(yue)媽媽佢…
(en)Mom, she...

270
00:19:44,746 --> 00:19:45,698
(yue)米卡莎…
(en)Mikasa...

271
00:19:51,877 --> 00:19:53,476
(yue)已經…已經冇喇
(en)It’s... it’s already gone

272
00:19:54,393 --> 00:19:56,962
(yue)呢個城市冇喇
(en)This city is gone

273
00:19:57,820 --> 00:20:00,414
(yue)呢度好快就會畀嗰啲巨人侵佔啊！
(en)This place will soon be overrun by Titans!

274
00:20:03,822 --> 00:20:04,973
(yue)唔好死吖
(en)Don’t die

275
00:20:06,568 --> 00:20:08,044
(yue)千祈唔好𢱕中我屋企
(en)Please don’t hit my house

276
00:20:08,527 --> 00:20:11,076
(yue)只要轉到個彎，就返到屋企！
(en)Just need to turn the corner, and I’ll be home!

277
00:20:16,472 --> 00:20:17,592
(yue)媽媽！
(en)Mom!

278
00:20:20,133 --> 00:20:21,093
(yue)媽媽！
(en)Mom!
279
00:20:23,219 --> 00:20:25,705
-艾倫  
-米卡莎，你幫我手抬嗰邊
(en)-Eren  
-Mikasa, help me lift this side

280
00:20:25,766 --> 00:20:27,320
(yue)一齊抬起條柱吖
(en)Lift the beam together

281
00:20:46,142 --> 00:20:48,172
-要快啲啊，米卡莎  
-知喇
(en)-Hurry up, Mikasa  
-I got it

282
00:20:49,259 --> 00:20:51,783
(yue)嗰啲巨人已經走咗入嚟啊
(en)The Titans have already entered

283
00:20:52,642 --> 00:20:54,831
(yue)艾倫，你快啲帶米卡莎走
(en)Eren, take Mikasa and get out of here

284
00:20:54,943 --> 00:20:55,847
(yue)快啲走吖
(en)Hurry up and go

285
00:20:56,332 --> 00:20:57,823
(yue)我都想快啲走啊！
(en)I want to leave too!

286
00:20:58,072 --> 00:20:59,985
(yue)所以媽媽你快啲出嚟吖！
(en)So, Mom, get out quickly!

287
00:21:00,763 --> 00:21:02,230
(yue)你唔好再嘥時間
(en)Stop wasting time

288
00:21:02,382 --> 00:21:04,096
(yue)媽媽啲腳壓斷咗
(en)Mom’s legs are crushed

289
00:21:04,691 --> 00:21:07,191
(yue)就算真係拉到我出嚟  
我都已經走唔郁
(en)Even if you pull me out, I can’t move

290
00:21:08,207 --> 00:21:09,151
(yue)明唔明啊？
(en)Do you understand?

291
00:21:09,219 --> 00:21:11,009
(yue)係噉嘅，我就孭住你走！
(en)If that’s the case, I’ll carry you on my back!

292
00:21:11,070 --> 00:21:13,609
(yue)點解你呢個仔成日都唔肯聽媽媽嘅説話？
(en)Why do you never listen to your mother?

293
00:21:14,534 --> 00:21:16,731
(yue)係咪我嘅遺言你都唔肯聽啊？
(en)Are you even going to ignore my final words?

294
00:21:17,470 --> 00:21:18,446
(yue)米卡莎
(en)Mikasa

295
00:21:21,350 --> 00:21:22,262
(yue)唔得！
(en)No!

296
00:21:23,096 --> 00:21:25,238
(yue)就係噉落去我哋都會…
(en)If this goes on, we’ll all...

297
00:21:27,191 --> 00:21:28,059
(yue)漢尼斯
(en)Hannes

298
00:21:30,286 --> 00:21:32,326
(yue)你快啲幫我帶佢哋兩個走啊
(en)Quickly, take both of them and go

299
00:21:33,667 --> 00:21:36,476
