305
00:22:12,296 --> 00:22:13,502
(yue)好多謝你
(en)Thank you so much

306
00:22:14,294 --> 00:22:15,512
(yue)媽媽未走㗎
(en)Mom’s still there

307
00:22:15,573 --> 00:22:16,462
(yue)媽媽！
(en)Mom!

308
00:22:16,818 --> 00:22:19,429
(yue)艾倫、米卡莎
(en)Eren, Mikasa

309
00:22:20,397 --> 00:22:22,056
(yue)要生存落去啊！
(en)You have to survive!

310
00:22:35,227 --> 00:22:36,636
(yue)唔好走吖…
(en)Don’t leave...

311
00:22:47,158 --> 00:22:49,454
(yue)唔好啊！
(en)No!

312
00:23:24,426 --> 00:23:28,089
(yue)嗰一日，人類記返起…
(en)That day, humanity remembered...

313
00:23:33,234 --> 00:23:35,415
(yue)一直畀佢哋支配嘅恐懼
(en)The fear that had always ruled over them

314
00:23:38,358 --> 00:23:40,650
(yue)同由如韞喺鳥籠入面嘅…
(en)And the humiliation of being trapped in a birdcage-like state...

